ory are peers who are treated equally and are given equal amounts of attention.", "The SAG Awards reminds you to follow the FTC Social Media Guidelines [16 C.F.R. \u2022", "Part 255].", "Please note: The performers union that presents the Screen Actors Guild Awards is SAG-AFTRA. Since", "the merger of Screen Actors Guild and the American Federation of Television and Radio Artists", "in 2012, SAG as a stand-alone entity no longer exists.", "Screen Actors Guild Awards\u00ae, LLC", "phone 323.549.6612 \u2022 email publicity@sagawards.org \u2022 web www.sagawards.org", "Airs Sunday, January 19, 2020 on TNT & TBS"], "bbox": [[0.365731, 0.159847, 0.31273600000000007, 0.019635], [0.259601, 0.186816, 0.524788, 0.019635], [0.058824, 0.223745, 0.81415, 0.015573], [0.125817, 0.240714, 0.7471810000000001, 0.015573], [0.125817, 0.257381, 0.747152, 0.015573], [0.125817, 0.274351, 0.438711, 0.015573], [0.058824, 0.306169, 0.81393, 0.015573], [0.125817, 0.323139, 0.747082, 0.015573], [0.125817, 0.340108, 0.7471619999999999, 0.015573], [0.125817, 0.357078, 0.085956, 0.015573], [0.125817, 0.389241, 0.12071700000000002, 0.019635], [0.155229, 0.426169, 0.679937, 0.015573], [0.184641, 0.443139, 0.6738649999999999, 0.015573], [0.184641, 0.459805, 0.32468499999999995, 0.015573], [0.155229, 0.484351, 0.310241, 0.015573], [0.155229, 0.508896, 0.5683209999999999, 0.015573], [0.155229, 0.533442, 0.7178390000000001, 0.015573], [0.184641, 0.550411, 0.6881120000000001, 0.015573], [0.184641, 0.567381, 0.6880580000000001, 0.015573], [0.184641, 0.584351, 0.13785600000000003, 0.015573], [0.155229, 0.608896, 0.6679730000000001, 0.015573], [0.184641, 0.625866, 0.43053900000000006, 0.015573], [0.155229, 0.650411, 0.677103, 0.015573], [0.184641, 0.667381, 0.677686, 0.015573], [0.184559, 0.691879, -0.020346000000000003, 0.017016], [0.184641, 0.708593, 0.07795099999999999, 0.015573], [0.058824, 0.739805, 0.814019, 0.015573], [0.125817, 0.756775, 0.7467619999999999, 0.015573], [0.125817, 0.773745, 0.428658